&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err-http2-session/"&gt;ERR_HTTP2_SESSION&lt;/a&gt; — HTTP/2 session error.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err-http2-stream/"&gt;ERR_HTTP2_STREAM_CLOSED&lt;/a&gt; — stream already closed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err_stream_destroyed/"&gt;ERR_STREAM_DESTROYED&lt;/a&gt; — stream destroyed.&lt;/li&gt;
